    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rust and Resolve is a 2D platforming game, developed with the intent to cause harm to desktop surfaces, monitors and other miscellaneous computer hardware. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as a small robot tasked with navigating the tricky environment in an attempt to find a way home.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Brave the climb alone, or team up with friends to tackle the punishing world together. Whether playing solo or cooperatively, the game already offers many hours of intense platforming action.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Developer Commentary</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;This is my first and only (as of release) Indie game.&quot; </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;My intent with this project is to develop a greater understanding of game design and development. I look forward to seeing how the community interacts with this game and, of course, hope that you have a great time playing.&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;Please note, this game is unfinished in its current state, I will be actively developing this project, and have may features  and changes in the works; The game features plenty of content in its current state and offers many hours of playtime&quot;</p>",
